    <text>
      <body>
        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName>The Nightingale Fund |5, Parliament Street</placeName>
                    <date>2 February 1856</date>
                    <salute>Dear Sir,</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
                  <p>I received with much satisfaction the contributions from your ??:</p>
                  <p>If the answer be small, the manner of collecting it is so gratifying as to increase its value two fold.</p>
                  <p>The touching remark you appended to your letter concerning the tranquil and peaceful death of your Mother, as contrasted with that of so many who have perished in the Crimea – is one that I shall keep to &amp; hold ????</p>
                  <p>I am Rev Sir | your faithful servant | S.C. Hall</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        
